#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.eval.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.eval"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.df_eval:1 of
msgid "Evaluate a string describing operations on DataFrame columns."
msgstr "对描述 DataFrame 列操作的字符串进行求值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.df_eval:3 of
msgid ""
"Operates on columns only, not specific rows or elements.  This allows "
"`eval` to run arbitrary code, which can make you vulnerable to code "
"injection if you pass user input to this function."
msgstr ""
"仅对列进行操作，不对特定行或元素进行操作。这使得 `eval` 可以运行任意代码"
"，如果您将用户输入传递给此函数，可能会导致代码注入漏洞。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.df_eval of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.df_eval:7 of
msgid "The expression string to evaluate."
msgstr "要求值的表达式字符串。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.df_eval:9 of
msgid ""
"If the expression contains an assignment, whether to perform the "
"operation inplace and mutate the existing DataFrame. Otherwise, a new "
"DataFrame is returned."
msgstr ""
"如果表达式包含赋值操作，是否就地执行操作并修改现有的 DataFrame。否则，将"
"返回一个新的 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.df_eval:13 of
msgid ""
"See the documentation for :func:`eval` for complete details on the "
"keyword arguments accepted by :meth:`~pandas.DataFrame.query`."
msgstr ""
"有关 :meth:`~pandas.DataFrame.query` 接受的关键字参数的完整详细信息，"
"请参阅 :func:`eval` 的文档。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.df_eval of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.df_eval:17 of
msgid "The result of the evaluation."
msgstr "求值的结果。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.df_eval of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.df_eval:22 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.query`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.df_eval:23 of
msgid "Evaluates a boolean expression to query the columns of a frame."
msgstr "对布尔表达式进行求值，以查询帧的列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.df_eval:25 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.assign`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.df_eval:26 of
msgid "Can evaluate an expression or function to create new values for a column."
msgstr "可以对表达式或函数进行求值，以为列创建新值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.df_eval:28 of
msgid ":py:obj:`eval`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.df_eval:29 of
msgid "Evaluate a Python expression as a string using various backends."
msgstr "使用各种后端将 Python 表达式作为字符串进行求值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.df_eval:32 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.df_eval:33 of
msgid ""
"For more details see the API documentation for :func:`~eval`. For "
"detailed examples see :ref:`enhancing performance with eval "
"<enhancingperf.eval>`."
msgstr ""
"有关更多详细信息，请参阅 :func:`~eval` 的 API 文档。有关详细示例，请参阅 "
":ref:`使用 eval 提高性能 <enhancingperf.eval>`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.df_eval:38 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.df_eval:56 of
msgid ""
"Assignment is allowed though by default the original DataFrame is not "
"modified."
msgstr "允许赋值操作，但默认情况下不会修改原始 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.df_eval:74 of
msgid "Use ``inplace=True`` to modify the original DataFrame."
msgstr "使用 ``inplace=True`` 修改原始 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.df_eval:85 of
msgid "Multiple columns can be assigned to using multi-line expressions:"
msgstr "可以使用多行表达式为多个列赋值："

